Interface IPatientDAO

All Superinterfaces:

PatientDAOHibernate
public interface IPatientDAO
extends IGenericDAO<Patient,java.lang.Long>

This interface describes how patient addition, deletion, and other CRUD functions are handled. At the present time, only PatientDAOHibernate.java implements this interface.
